Booking reference 
TESTRF  
  

Hi Test Passenger, 

 is waiting for you.

We want to help you prepare for your journey so here are some of our suggestions. The first thing is to leave some room in your luggage to bring some unforgettable moments and the desire to continue your travels. 

  


1 . Do you have everything you need? 
Confirm all the details of your booking and the time when check-in opens. 
See your booking here and, if possible, check-in online at flytap.com or through the App.   


Check-in Online available:  36 hours prior flight departure time 



