All times are local times at the departure airport.  In high density flights it might be necessary to ship hand luggage in the plane cargo hold due to the reduced cabin space  https://tap-rt-prod1-t.campaign.adobe.com/r/?id=tba8998b,ce32f9e,6a0168a Know more . 

  


