2.  Useful information and some precautions to keep in mind. 



  
  


Time Zone  Lisboa



  
  


  

  
  

Documents 

Make sure that you have all the necessary documents such as your Identification card or passport and that they are still valid for your journey. 

  

 https://tap-rt-prod1-t.campaign.adobe.com/r/?id=tba8998b,ce32f9e,6a01690 See More   
  
  
  
  

3.  Catch up on your reading during the flight! 

  
  

Digital Kiosk 

Use the digital kiosk. It is a free service on the TAP Air Portugal App that allows you to download newspapers or other publications to your tablet or smartphone. 

  
 https://tap-rt-prod1-t.campaign.adobe.com/r/?id=tba8998b,ce32f9e,6a01693      https://tap-rt-prod1-t.campaign.adobe.com/r/?id=tba8998b,ce32f9e,6a01694   
  
  

We hope you have a good journey on TAP Air Portugal. 

  

